OL,3,C"It was terrifying"
OL,5,FMartin Hibbert and his daughter Eve
OL,6,Fsued Richard Hall for harassment in
OL,7,Fthe High Court and were awarded
OL,8,F#45,000 in damages on Friday.
OL,10,FThe father-of-one was left with a
OL,11,Fspinal cord injury and Ms Hibbert
OL,12,Fsuffered severe brain damage as a
OL,13,Fresult of the 2017 bombing - which
OL,14,FHall had described as "a lie".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
