OL,3,C"It was terrifying"
OL,5,FMr Hibbert, of Chorley, Lancashire,
OL,6,Fsaid "It's been tough having to deal
OL,7,Fwith the injuries not just to myself
OL,8,Fbut to my daughter, the most precious
OL,9,Fthing in my life. It was like a double
OL,10,Fblow. Just dealing with that and
OL,11,Fliving with a spinal cord injury is
OL,12,Ftough enough but then having to deal
OL,13,Fwith the constant abuse on social
OL,14,Fmedia and having it in the background
OL,15,Fall the time. It has been five six
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
