OL,3,C"It was terrifying"
OL,5,F"Then to find out he had taken it even
OL,6,Ffurther and had filmed Eve outside the
OL,7,Fhouse. It had to be stopped. Friday
OL,8,Fwas a really tough day to get through
OL,9,Fbut it was vindication in a way that
OL,10,Feverything we have had to put up with.
OL,11,FIt wasn't right. It was harassment.
OL,12,FThe judge agreed with that.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
