OL,3,C"It was terrifying"
OL,5,F"It was terrifying and I found out at
OL,6,Fa time when I was giving evidence at
OL,7,Fthe inquiry back in 2021 so it was a
OL,8,Ftough time anyway. The police came
OL,9,Fround to where Eve lives to check the
OL,10,Fgarden because he said that he had
OL,11,Fhidden a camera disguised as a tree or
OL,12,Fa bush but then he didn't capture the
OL,13,Fvideo that he wanted so then he parked
OL,14,Foutside the house and filmed her and
OL,15,Fsaw her in a wheelchair with a carer
OL,16,Fand went on his website and declared
OL,17,Fhe had got this footage. The police
OL,18,Fwere concerned about that.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
