OL,3,C"It was terrifying"
OL,5,F"I had a lot to focus on at the time
OL,6,Fand I had to keep quiet about it for
OL,7,Ftwelve months which was a really tough
OL,8,Fthing to do while all these videos are
OL,9,Fbeing posted. It was tough.
OL,11,FTwenty-two people died and hundreds
OL,12,Fmore were injured when suicide bomber
OL,13,FSalman Abedi detonated a homemade
OL,14,Fdevice in the foyer of the venue as
OL,15,Fcrowds left an Ariana Grande concert.
OL,17,FHall had told the court his claims
OL,18,Fwere in the public interest as a
OL,19,Fjournalist and claimed "millions of
OL,20,Fpeople" had "bought a lie" about the
OL,21,Fattack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
