OL,3,C"It was terrifying"
OL,5,FMartin is now hoping to bring out
OL,6,FEve's Law so that others are protected
OL,7,Fin the future.
OL,9,FHe said "I can't give a clear
OL,10,Fdefinition of what it is but in the
OL,11,Frun-up to the trial I thought Eve's
OL,12,FLaw would be a law to protect others
OL,13,Fwho are involved in tragedies from
OL,14,Fconspiracy theorists and hate online.
OL,15,FWhat the trial proved was the law can
OL,16,Fcope with this.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
