OL,3,C"It was terrifying"
OL,5,F"Eve's Law could well be the access to
OL,6,Fjustice for people. We have seen what
OL,7,Fit cost for me to do this. You are
OL,8,Flooking at #260,000. It's impossible
OL,9,Ffor anyone to afford that so I am
OL,10,Fthinking a panel of pro bono
OL,11,Fbarristers that can help the public to
OL,12,Ftake these people down. If that is the
OL,13,Flegacy that would be something quite
OL,14,Fbeautiful to come out of it."
OL,16,FIn a judgment in October, Mrs Justice
OL,17,FSteyn ruled in favour of the Hibberts
OL,18,Fand described Mr Hall's behaviour as
OL,19,F"a negligent, indeed reckless, abuse
OL,20,Fof media freedom".
