OL,3,C"It was terrifying"
OL,5,FAt a hearing on Friday 8 November, the
OL,6,Fjudge said Mr Hibbert and his daughter
OL,7,Fwould each be awarded #22,500 in
OL,8,Fdamages. Mr Hall was also told to pay
OL,9,F90% of the Hibberts' legal costs.
OL,11,FThe final figure may be determined by
OL,12,Fa specialist judge if an agreement is
OL,13,Fnot reached, but the court heard their
OL,14,Ftotal is currently estimated at
OL,15,F#260,000.
OL,17,FJonathan Price, for the pair, said Mr
OL,18,FHall's behaviour was "towards the more
OL,19,Foppressive end of the spectrum of
OL,20,Fharassing conduct".
